title: FDHypno-Audio_Compilation_3
description:
Ten more enchantresses and goddesses etc. - part 3 of 4. 
Featuring Lycia, Jenifahr, Kiss of Darkness - some of the names get a little silly - and various others. I quite like Jenifahr who is young and English. Best of all, she gives her mp3 files free on her website, sleepformenow.co.uk. 
Lady Julia is also non-commercial and very good. She also offers some very sensible advice on her website about using these files and also has a discussion group - on Yahoo, I think. Details of the various hypnodomme websites can be found on hypnoladies.com although they don&#039;t approve of P2P sharing. Not even slightly!
